  "Two cell phone plans are being compared. Plan A costs $30 per month plus $0.10 per text. Plan B costs $20 per month plus $0.20 per text. The equation 30 + 0.10t = 20 + 0.20t represents when they cost the same. After how many texts are the plans equal?": "",
